    "en": {
      "title": "Money placed in puja is magic",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna - Two persons have robbed 10 lakh rupees from Kota Muniappar Temple yesterday to invest in the business.",
        "A person from Jaffna has given 10 lakhs of rupees to the priest to invest in the new business venture he was about to start.",
        "Later, two people who were standing there in the middle of bringing the money taken from the puja out of the temple grabbed the money and ran away.",
        "A complaint has been registered at the Jaffna Police Station regarding the incident. Based on the complaint, the police have initiated investigations. (R)"
      ],
